OL,3,CAlcohol-free beer on draught 'helps
OL,4,Cpeople make healthy choices'
OL,6,FOffering alcohol-free options is often
OL,7,Fseen as a good alternative for people
OL,8,Fwho want to be healthier.
OL,10,FFor the new study, researchers from
OL,11,Fthe university's Tobacco and Alcohol
OL,12,FResearch Group, working with Bristol
OL,13,FCity Council, recruited 14 pubs and
OL,14,Fbars in Bristol.
OL,16,FNone of the venues had previously
OL,17,Foffered alcohol-free beer on draught.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
