OL,6,FHowever, this was replaced by an
OL,7,Fequivalent increase in sales of
OL,8,Falcohol-free beer, suggesting
OL,9,Fcustomers were choosing the healthier
OL,10,Foption.
OL,12,FFurthermore, there was no impact on
OL,13,Fthe money taken, suggesting the change
OL,14,Fdid not leave pubs and bars worse off.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/12
