OL,6,FProfessor of behavioural science Ivo
OL,7,FVlaev, from Warwick Business School,
OL,8,Fsaid the "study underscores the power
OL,9,Fof nudges in shaping healthier
OL,10,Fsocietal choices".
OL,12,FHe added: "By simply making alcohol-
OL,13,Ffree beer more visible and accessible
OL,14,F` essentially altering the choice
OL,15,Farchitecture in bars and pubs ` the
OL,16,Fresearch leverages basic human biases
OL,17,Ftowards easier, more prominent
OL,18,Foptions."
