OL,6,FMatt Lambert, health information and
OL,7,Fpromotion manager at the World Cancer
OL,8,FResearch Fund, said it was
OL,9,F"encouraging to see that making
OL,10,Falcohol-free beer more visible to
OL,11,Fconsumers led them to make a healthier
OL,12,Fchoice by choosing the alcohol-free
OL,13,Foption".
OL,15,FHowever, he added: "Just like with
OL,16,Falcoholic drinks, the sugar and
OL,17,Fcalories in alcohol-free options can
OL,18,Fvary.
