OL,6,F"That's why it's best for your health
OL,7,Fif you opt for smaller sizes ` so,
OL,8,Frather than a pint, choose a bottle or
OL,9,Fhave a half-pint."
OL,11,FMatt Lambert, chief executive of The
OL,12,FPortman Group, said: "We welcome the
OL,13,Ffindings of this study which highlight
OL,14,Fthe importance of venues voluntarily
OL,15,Fincreasing the availability of low and
OL,16,Fno alcohol alternatives and
OL,17,Fnormalising these products.
