OL,3,CAlcohol-free beer on draught 'helps
OL,4,Cpeople make healthy choices'
OL,6,F"This also reinforces our own research
OL,7,Fwhich shows these products are a vital
OL,8,Ftool in helping people moderate their
OL,9,Fdrinking and reducing wider alcohol
OL,10,Fharms such as binge drinking and drink
OL,11,Fdriving."
OL,13,FIt comes as researchers at the
OL,14,FUniversity of York said there is not
OL,15,Fyet enough data on consumer behaviour
OL,16,Faround no- and low-alcohol drinks to
OL,17,Fstate they are a healthy alternative
OL,18,Fto alcohol.
