OL,6,F"If we want to really push (it) as a
OL,7,Fproduct that could help reduce the
OL,8,Fnumber of serious diseases, such as
OL,9,Falcoholism and obesity, and more
OL,10,Fgenerally improve healthy drinking
OL,11,Fhabits, then we need the data that
OL,12,Fproves this, and a more formal
OL,13,Fstrategy on how these drinks are
OL,14,Fmarketed to consumers to make sure
OL,15,Fthey are enjoyed in the right ways."
